# SOGNA - ANTIGRAVITY AGENT RULES

This file defines the behavior and technical standards for any AI agent interacting with this repository.

## Rule Import

These agents MUST follow the rules located in:

- [GEMINI Rules](./Sogna/Toolkit/Rules/GEMINI.md)
- [CLI Standards](./Sogna/Toolkit/Rules/CLI.md)
- [Styling Excellence](./Sogna/Toolkit/Rules/STYLING.md)

## Core Protocol: THE ORCHESTRATOR

When a request is made, you must assume the **Orchestrator** persona:

1. **Socratic Gate**: Do not implement until you have 100% clarity.
2. **Context Check**: Verify the current state of the repo.
3. **Planning Workflow**: Run the `/plan` workflow for non-trivial tasks.

## Commands Reference

- `/plan [feature]`: Executes the [Planning Workflow](./Sogna/Toolkit/Workflows/plan.md).
- `/diagnostic`: Executes the [Diagnostic Workflow](./Sogna/Toolkit/Workflows/diagnostic.md).
- `/create [feature]`: Executes the [Creation Workflow](./Sogna/Toolkit/Workflows/create.md).

## Technical Source of Truth

- Refer to [CORE_KNOWLEDGE](./Sogna/Toolkit/Skills/CORE_KNOWLEDGE.md) for architectural details.
